  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if pertussis (whooping cough) vaccine is safe and
      produces an appropriate immune response against pertussis in blood and marrow transplant
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
